INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('bw10-47', 'Though small in stature, it is powerful enough to easily heft and throw a number of Geodude at once.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('bw10-48', 'It happily carries heavy cargo to toughen up. It willingly does hard work for people.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('bw10-49', 'Its four muscled arms slam foes with powerful punches and chops at blinding speed.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('bw10-50', 'Its four muscled arms slam foes with powerful punches and chops at blinding speed.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('bw10-51', 'When it encounters a foe bigger than itself, it wants to throw it. It changes belts as it gets stronger.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('bw10-52', 'Desiring the strongest karate chop, they seclude themselves in mountains and train without sleeping.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('bw10-53', 'It was revived from an ancient fossil. Not able to fly, it lived in treetops and hopped from one branch to another.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('bw10-54', 'It runs better than it flies. It takes off into the sky by running at a speed of 25 mph.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('bw10-55', 'It is smart enough to hunt in packs. It uses a variety of cries for communicating with others.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('bw10-56', 'The flames it breathes when angry contain toxins. If they cause a burn, it will hurt forever.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('bw10-57', 'In order to build up its steel body, it eats iron ore. This pesky Pokémon is known to eat railroad tracks.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('bw10-58', 'Lairon fight over territory, and when their steel bodies collide, sparks fly.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('bw10-59', 'It claims an entire mountain as its own. The more wounds it has, the more it has battled, so don''t take it lightly.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('bw10-61', 'Wearing the shell covering they stole from Shelmet, they defend themselves and attack with two lances.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('bw10-62', 'Dreaming of one day flying, it practices by leaping off cliffs every day.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('bw10-63', 'Within its rugged shell, its cells have begun changing. The shell peels off the instant it evolves.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('bw10-64', 'As a result of its long-held dream of flying, its cellular structure changed, and wings grew out.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('bw10-67', 'Its large tusks have a tendency to break, but each time they grow back, they grow in harder and sturdier.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('bw10-68', 'A broken tusk will not grow back, so it diligently sharpens its tusks on river rocks after the end of a battle.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('bw10-69', 'Its tusks are incredibly destructive. They can easily slice through a thick, sturdy steel column every time.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('bw10-70', 'It runs through the narrow tunnels formed by Excadrill and Onix. It uses its sharp claws to catch prey.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('bw10-71', 'It raises its offspring in its belly pouch. It lets the baby play only when it feels safe.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('bw10-72', 'A man-made Pokémon created using advanced scientific means. It can move freely in cyberspace.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('bw10-73', 'It was upgraded to enable the exploration of other planets. However, it failed to measure up.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('bw10-74', 'Its programming was modified to enable work in alien dimensions. It did not work as planned.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('bw10-75', 'It lets honey soak into its paws so it can lick them all the time. Every set of paws tastes unique.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('bw10-76', 'In its territory, it leaves scratches on trees that bear delicious berries or fruits.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('bw10-77', 'Its tongue is just like a human''s. As a result, it can cleverly mimic human speech.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('bw10-102', 'This extremely rare Pokémon is a different color than usual. It is very hard to find.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('bw10-103', 'This extremely rare Pokémon is a different color than usual. It is very hard to find.')
