INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp3-92', 'It looks like an aquatic plant and serves as a ferry to Pokémon that can''t swim.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp3-93', 'Born in the spout of a volcano, its body is covered by flames that shimmer like the sun.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp3-94', 'Its fluffy coat swells to double when static electricity builds up. Touching it can be shocking.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp3-96', 'It picks food from cactus plants, deftly avoiding buds and spines. It seems to skip about to move.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp3-97', 'It scans its surroundings by raising its ears out of the grass. Its toxic horn is for protection.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp3-98', 'It is strong despite its compact size. It can easily pick up and carry an adult human on its back.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp3-99', 'It is docile and prefers to avoid conflict. If disturbed, however, it can ferociously strike back.')
