INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp3-101', 'It shoots the poison spines on its body in all directions. Its round form makes it a poor swimmer.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp3-102', 'It uses the thorns on its head to sense human emotions. It is said to appear in front of cheerful people.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp3-103', 'Cautious in the extreme, its hardy vitality lets it live in any kind of environment.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp3-104', 'It has a very nervous nature. It stands up high on its tail so it can scan wide areas.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp3-105', 'It swims backwards by opening and closing its two shells. Its large tongue is always kept hanging out.')
