INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp4-87', 'It is shrouded by blue vines. No one has seen the face hidden behind this growth of vines.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp4-88', 'Its shell is said to be stuffed with happiness that it shares with kindhearted people.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp4-89', 'A fire burns inside, so it feels very warm to hug. It launches fireballs of 1,800 degrees F.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp4-90', 'The soles of its feet are covered by countless tiny spikes, enabling it to walk on walls and ceilings.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp4-91', 'Shaped like ancient writing, it is a huge mystery whether language or UNOWN came first.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp4-92', 'It communicates with others by lighting up its rear at night. It loves ILLUMISE''s sweet aroma.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp4-93', 'It eats its weight in leaves every day. It fends off attackers with the needle on its head.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp4-94', 'Usually, its cries are like quiet murmurs.  If frightened, it shrieks at the same volume as a jet plane.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp4-95', 'It makes its nest on steep sea cliffs. Riding updrafts, it soars to great heights.')
