INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp5-51', 'It uses its tail to pluck fruits that are out of reach. Its tail is more adept than its real hands.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp5-52', 'X-ray photos were taken to check its body structure. Nothing appeared, however.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp5-53', 'When it senses danger, it perks up its ears. On cold nights, it sleeps with its head tucked into its fur.')
