INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp5-55', 'It can learn and speak human words. If they gather, they all learn the same saying.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp5-56', 'Its fiery rear end is fueled by gas made in its belly. Even rain can''t extinguish the fire.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp5-58', 'It emits cries by agitating an orb at the back of its throat. It moves with flouncing hops.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp5-59', 'It collects and delivers honey to its colony. At night, they cluster to form a beehive and sleep.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp5-60', 'Inflating its poison sacs, it makes an eerie blubbering sound for intimidation.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp5-61', 'It tugs on the hands of children to steal them away. However, it gets pulled around instead.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp5-62', 'A rare Pokémon that adapts to harsh environments by taking on different evolutionary forms.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp5-63', 'A rare Pokémon that adapts to harsh environments by taking on different evolutionary forms.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp5-64', 'Using electricity stored in its fur, it stimulates its muscles to heighten its reaction speed.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp5-65', 'With its sharp glare, it puts foes in a mild hypnotic state. It is a very fickle Pokémon.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp5-66', 'It enshrouds itself with sand to protect itself from germs. It does not enjoy getting wet.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp5-67', 'It is thought to have inhabited beaches 300 million years ago. It is protected by a stiff shell.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp5-68', 'It hides food under its long body hair. However, it forgets it has hidden the food.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp5-69', 'A Pokémon that was resurrected from a fossil using modern science. It swam in ancient seas.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp5-70', 'If it looses crackling power from the electric pouches on its cheeks, it is being wary.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp5-71', 'It lives along shores in northern countries. A skilled swimmer, it dives for over 10 minutes to hunt.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp5-73', 'It lives along bodies of water. Its body shape changed to suit its habitat.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp5-74', 'It flaps its small wings busily to fly. Using its beak, it searches in grass for prey.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp5-75', 'Usually with a large flock, it is barely noticeable when alone. Its cries are very strident.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp5-76', 'It sprays a nose-curling, stinky fluid from its rear to repel attackers.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp5-77', 'It undertakes photosynthesis with its body, making oxygen. The leaf on its head wilts if it is thirsty.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp6-1', 'An alien virus that fell to earth on a meteor underwent a DNA mutation to become this Pokémon.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp6-2', 'It is said to make its home somewhere in the sea. It guides crews of shipwrecks to shore.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp6-3', 'It freezes foes with an icy breath nearly -60 degrees F. What seems to be its body is actually hollow.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp6-4', 'A Pokémon that is said to live in a world on the reverse side of ours. It appears in an ancient cemetery.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp6-5', 'It observes prey while hanging inverted from branches. When the chance presents itself, it swoops!')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp6-6', 'It dwells in volcanic caves. It digs in with its cross-shaped feet to crawl on ceilings and walls.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp6-7', 'It lives in caves on the seafloor and creates giant whirlpools every time it moves.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp6-8', 'It has eyes that can see through anything. It spots and captures prey hiding behind objects.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp6-9', 'Its impressive tusks are made of ice. The population thinned when it turned warm after the ice age.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp6-10', 'Metang combined to form it. With four brains, it has the intelligence of a supercomputer.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('dp6-11', 'A Pokémon created by recombining Mew''s genes. It''s said to have the most savage heart among Pokémon.')
