INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('sm12-118', 'When it tightens its belt, it becomes stronger. Wild Throh use vines to weave their own belts.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('sm12-119', 'It follows Pangoro around like a henchman. When Pancham makes a big mistake, its leaf gets taken away.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('sm12-120', 'This rowdy Pokémon boasts great physical strength. Many Trainers are also smitten by its lively character.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('sm12-121', 'Its hard pincers are well suited to both offense and defense. Fights between two Crabrawler are like boxing matches.')
