INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('sm12-125', 'They use their saliva to stick leaves to their shoulders. You can tell what troop they belong to from the position of the leaves.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('sm12-126', 'It likes the shovel on its head, so Sandygast will get serious and fight any children who come to take it back.')
