INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('sm5-22', 'It uses ceilings and walls to launch aerial attacks. Its fiery tail is but one weapon.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('sm5-23', 'It tosses its enemies around with agility. It uses all its limbs to fight in its own unique style.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('sm5-24', 'Its body is composed of plasma. It is known to infiltrate electronic devices and wreak havoc.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('sm5-25', 'Volcanoes or dry, craggy places are its home. It emanates a sweet-smelling poisonous gas that attracts bug Pokémon, then attacks them.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('sm5-26', 'Filled with pheromones, its poisonous gas can be diluted to use in the production of luscious perfumes.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('sm5-27', 'It gushes fire and poisonous gases from its nostrils. Its dung is an explosive substance and can be put to various uses.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('sm5-28', 'An ancient tradition of Alolan festivals, still carried on to this day, is a competition to slide Sandshrew across ice as far as one can.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('sm5-29', 'This Pokémon''s steel spikes are sheathed in ice. Stabs from these spikes cause deep wounds and severe frostbite as well.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('sm5-30', 'It exhales air colder than -58 degrees Fahrenheit. Elderly people in Alola call this Pokémon by an older name—Keokeo.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('sm5-31', 'Because it is very proud, it hates accepting food from people. Its thick down guards it from cold.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('sm5-32', 'Because it is very proud, it hates accepting food from people. Its thick down guards it from cold.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('sm5-33', 'It lives a solitary life. Its wings deliver wicked blows that can snap even the thickest of trees.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('sm5-34', 'The three horns that extend from its beak attest to its power. The leader has the biggest horns.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('sm5-35', 'It inflates the flotation sac around its neck and pokes its head out of the water to see what is going on.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('sm5-36', 'Its flotation sac developed as a result of pursuing aquatic prey. It can double as a rubber raft.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('sm5-37', 'In the spring, it grows berries with the texture of frozen treats around its belly.')
