INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('sm5-111', 'The blooming of Gracidea flowers confers the power of flight upon it. Feelings of gratitude are the message it delivers.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('sm5-112', 'It wanders around in a never-ending search for food. At dusk, it collapses from exhaustion and falls asleep on the spot.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('sm5-113', 'It adores having Rattata and Raticate for dinner, but as it''s diurnal, it never encounters them. This Pokémon boasts incredible patience.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('sm5-114', 'Deep in the jungle, high in the lofty canopy, this Pokémon abides. On rare occasions, it shows up at the beach to match wits with Slowking.')
