INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('xy11-73', 'Its red core functions as an energy tank. It fires the charged energy through its spikes into an area.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('xy11-74', 'It has a body and heart of steel. It worked with its allies to punish people when they hurt Pokémon.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('xy11-76', 'The tip of its tail is filled with oil that is lighter than water, so it acts as a float.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('xy11-77', 'The bubble-like pattern on its stomach helps it camouflage itself when it''s in the water.')
