INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('xy12-11', 'Its wings can carry this Pokémon close to an altitude of 4,600 feet. It blows out fire at very high temperatures.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('xy12-14', 'While young, it has six gorgeous tails. When it grows, several new tails are sprouted.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('xy12-15', 'It has nine long tails and fur that gleams gold. It is said to live for 1,000 years.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('xy12-17', 'Very friendly and faithful to people. It will try to repel enemies by barking and biting.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('xy12-18', 'A Pokémon that is described in Chinese legends. It is said to race at an unbelievable speed.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('xy12-19', 'Its body is light, and its legs are incredibly powerful. It can clear Ayers Rock in one leap.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('xy12-20', 'Found near the mouth of a volcano. This fire-breather''s body temperature is nearly 2,200 degrees Fahrenheit.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('xy12-23', 'Its slick black skin is thin and damp. A part of its internal organs can be seen through the skin as a spiral pattern.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('xy12-24', 'Its two legs are well developed. Even though it can live on the ground, it prefers living in water.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('xy12-25', 'An adept swimmer, it knows the front crawl, butterfly, and more. It is faster than the best human swimmers.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('xy12-28', 'Covered with light blue fur, its hide is thick and tough. It is active in bitter cold of -40 degrees Fahrenheit.')
