INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('xy12-30', 'It appears in large numbers by seashores. At night, its central core flashes with a red light.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('xy12-31', 'This Pokémon has a geometric body. Because of its body, the locals suspect that it is an alien creature.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('xy12-33', 'It is virtually worthless in terms of both power and speed. It is the most weak and pathetic Pokémon in the world.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('xy12-34', 'It has an extremely aggressive nature. The Hyper Beam it shoots from its mouth totally incinerates all targets.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('xy12-35', 'It has small electric sacs on both its cheeks. If threatened, it looses electric charges from the sacs.')
