INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('xy12-38', 'A linked cluster formed of several Magnemite. It discharges powerful magnetic waves at high voltage.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('xy12-39', 'A life-form whose identity is unknown. It is said to Screech or suddenly Self-Destruct.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('xy12-40', 'It explodes in response to even minor stimuli. It is feared, with the nickname of "The Bomb Ball."')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('xy12-41', 'It loves to feed on strong electricity. It occasionally appears around large power plants and so on.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('xy12-42', 'One of the legendary bird Pokémon. While it is flying, it makes crackling and snapping sounds.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('xy12-43', 'Its large ears are flapped like wings when it is listening to distant sounds. It extends toxic barbs when angered.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('xy12-44', 'It is easily angered. By swinging its well-developed horn wildly, it can even punch through diamond.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('xy12-45', 'It is recognized by its rock-hard hide and its extended horn. Be careful with the horn as it contains venom.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('xy12-47', 'A being that exists as a thin gas. It can topple an Indian elephant by enveloping the prey in two seconds.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('xy12-48', 'If you get the feeling of being watched in darkness when nobody is around, Haunter is there.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('xy12-49', 'A descendant of the legendary animal baku, which is said to eat dreams. It is skilled at hypnotism.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('xy12-50', 'Its thin, balloon-like body is inflated by horribly toxic gases. It reeks when it is nearby.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('xy12-51', 'A Pokémon whose genetic code was repeatedly recombined for research. It turned vicious as a result.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('xy12-53', 'So rare that it is still said to be a mirage by many experts. Only a few people have seen it worldwide.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('xy12-54', 'It burrows and lives underground. If threatened, it curls itself up into a ball for protection.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('xy12-55', 'It burrows through the ground at a shallow depth. It leaves raised earth in its wake, making it easy to spot.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('xy12-56', 'In battle, it digs through the ground and strikes the unsuspecting foe from an unexpected direction.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('xy12-57', 'Its whole body is composed of muscles. Even though it''s the size of a human child, it can hurl 100 grown-ups.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('xy12-58', 'Its formidable body never gets tired. It helps people by doing work such as the moving of heavy goods.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('xy12-59', 'Its four ruggedly developed arms can launch a flurry of 1,000 punches in just two seconds.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('xy12-61', 'It usually lives underground. It searches for food while boring its way through the ground at 50 miles per hour.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('xy12-62', 'The spirit of a pro boxer has infused this Pokémon. It throws punches that are faster than a bullet train.')
INSERT FLAVORTEXT VALUES ('xy12-63', 'Its adorable appearance makes it popular as a pet. However, it is rare and difficult to find.')
